AQUARAMA CO. v. OLD MILL CO. et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 30, 1903.) No. 98. Appeal from tbe Circuit Court of tbe United States for tbe Eastern District of New York. Edward Hymes, for appellants. Wm. H. Kenyon, for appellee.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and TOWNSEND, Circuit Judges.

PEE CUELAM.

Affirmed in open court. See 115 Fed. 806, 53 C. C. A. 376.
